#: ../create_a_story.rst:35
msgid "This is a happy Monkey named **Harley**."
msgstr ""

#: ../create_a_story.rst:37
msgid ""
"In the lower right corner of the Scratch, there are two areas-the "
"character area and the stage area, where we can add the sprites and stage"
" we want."
msgstr ""

#: ../create_a_story.rst:43
msgid ""
"First the current sprite, and then click the **Choose a Sprite** button "
"to add the sprite."
msgstr ""

#: ../create_a_story.rst:45
msgid ""
"Here we need to find Monkey, click on it! You can use the search box "
"above to find it. Here we give it a name **Harley**."
msgstr ""

#: ../create_a_story.rst:52
msgid "Harley is hungry. He asked his friend Perry where is the banana?"
msgstr ""

#: ../create_a_story.rst:54
msgid ""
"Click on your Harley sprite, and then click on the Event category. Drag "
"「**when ⚑ clicked**」 to the coding area on the right."
msgstr ""

#: ../create_a_story.rst:60
msgid ""
"Click on the Looks category and drag 「**say \"Hello!\" for 2 second**」 to"
" the bottom of \"when ⚑ clicked\"."
msgstr ""

#: ../create_a_story.rst:66
msgid "Change what it says and how long it says in the input box."
msgstr ""

#: ../create_a_story.rst:73
msgid "Perry had seen bananas in the park, so he told Harley."
msgstr ""

#: ../create_a_story.rst:75
msgid "Perry is a Frog, add Frog sprite and Forest backdrop."
msgstr ""

#: ../create_a_story.rst:81
msgid ""
"Click on the Frog sprite, add a 3 second 「**delay**」 block (wait for "
"Harley to finish speaking), and then it speaks."
msgstr ""

#: ../create_a_story.rst:87
msgid "Now, click on the green flag, we can see Harley and Perry chat."
msgstr ""

#: ../create_a_story.rst:90
msgid "Harley went to the park and found bananas on the table."
msgstr ""

#: ../create_a_story.rst:92
msgid ""
"Now, click on the Backdrop and let it switch after 6 seconds (after the "
"conversation ends)."
msgstr ""

#: ../create_a_story.rst:98
msgid ""
"Now, by clicking on the green flag, we can see that the Perry and Harley "
"\"come\" to the park together after the conversation."
msgstr ""

#: ../create_a_story.rst:104
msgid ""
"But Harley should come to the park alone, and there should be bananas on "
"the table. So, we have to make Perry \"disappear\"."
msgstr ""

#: ../create_a_story.rst:106
msgid ""
"Click on the Frog sprite, add an event, 「**when backdrop switches "
"to...**」, and find \"hide\" and \"show\" in Looks. Let the Perry appear "
"at the right time!"
msgstr ""

#: ../create_a_story.rst:112
msgid "Add the Banana sprite and adjust the angle."
msgstr ""

#: ../create_a_story.rst:118
msgid "Also let it appear at the right time."
msgstr ""

#: ../create_a_story.rst:124
msgid "Now, click on the green flag and you can see a complete story."
msgstr ""

